title: DDFP 418: Week 17 Review & Super Bowl Contenders
itunes:title: DDFP 418: Week 17 Review & Super Bowl Contenders
description:
Shek sits down with Ike Taylor, Maurice Jones-Drew, Handsome Hank, and Marcas Grant to breakdown all of Week 17 action, as well as preparing for playoffs. Do JJ Watt and Aaron Rodgers have a chance? Will it be another Seahawks vs Patriots Super Bowl? Is Cam Newton really better than Tom Brady? Find out more on DDFP. Watch the video show here (after 6pm EST): https://youtu.be/_YMX6NLZ8MU
